    <sect3 role="installation">
      <title>Installation of flit_core</title>

      <para>
        Build the <application>flit_core</application> part of
        the module:
      </para>

<screen><userinput>cd flit_core &amp;&amp;
pip3 wheel -w dist --no-build-isolation --no-deps $PWD</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      This package does not come with a test suite.
    </para>

    <para>
      Now, as the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> user:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>pip3 install --no-index --find-links dist --no-cache-dir --no-user flit_core</userinput></screen>

    </sect3>

